---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Results | Stackbase Directory Outcomes" description="Evidence-first results snapshot from Stackbase directory projects, including launch status and verifiable SEO context.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">RESULTS SNAPSHOT</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Real project outcomes, shown with evidence-first context</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">This page summarizes available outcomes from Stackbase projects. No inflated promises, no fabricated growth charts — only metrics and status we can stand behind publicly.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-4">IndoorClimbingGym</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• 7.5K URLs</li><li>• 1.78K indexed pages</li><li>• 4.1K organic keywords</li><li>• 1.68K clicks / 463K impressions (3 months)</li><li>• 531 AI-cited pages</li></ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a] mt-4">Metrics context date: Feb 24, 2026</p>
        <a href="/case-studies/indoorclimbinggym" class="inline-flex mt-5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-[#2a2a3a] text-white">Read full case study</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-4">GolfSimMap</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Launched Feb 12, 2026</li><li>• Early growth stage (new project)</li><li>• SEO-ready technical base deployed</li><li>• Expansion phase currently in progress</li></ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a] mt-4">Traffic data intentionally not overclaimed while early</p>
        <a href="/case-studies/golfsimmap" class="inline-flex mt-5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-[#2a2a3a] text-white">Read launch case study</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What this means for potential clients</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-[#c7c7d2]"><p>• Stackbase can deliver technically credible directory foundations</p><p>• SEO architecture is implemented from launch, not bolted on later</p><p>• Reporting stance is conservative and trust-first</p><p>• Scope recommendations are based on project stage, not hype</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">See full portfolio</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">Start your project</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
